Text: Hi Kristen, I am the husband of Melissa Bemer (Steve) who had arranged for me to drop off Lucy tomorrow and pick her up Sunday . I had a change of plans and wanted to see if we could adjust the schedule. I would be dropping her off around between 4 to 5p.m. this Friday and picking her up Sunday around 2pm. So just a shortened duration if that works with your schedule

Hey there, thats no problem to adjust. A Friday drop off between 4-5 works for me as does the pickup time. With those updates her Lucy’s stay total would be $100. I had sent Melissa my venmo info prior but can send to you if needed
Yes please share and thank you for the adjustment
Haha she asked for a Lucy update !
Is it possible for me to bring Lucy by within the hour for drop off? If not, the earlier availability on your end?
Sure, you can bring her within the next hour just shoot me a text when you’re headed my way and submit payment prior to drop off please
Ok leaving now. 15 minutes and sending $100 via Venmo
Unless the price changed then please provide new $ amount
As I know I adjusted drop off. Thank you!
